text: Arthur Shannos was a weightlifter from Australia. Arthur competed at the 1960 Summer Olympics and the 1964 Summer Olympics. He was born on 4 March 1938 and died on 1 September 2002.Arthur Shannos == References == Category:1938 births Category:2002 deaths Category:Olympians for Australia Category:Australian weightlifters Category:Sportspeople from Brisbane
